    q: "Git rebase vs merge khác nhau? Khi nào dùng gì?",
    a: "Merge: tạo merge commit, giữ history đầy đủ, safe cho shared branches. Rebase: rewrite history thành linear, clean hơn, KHÔNG dùng cho shared branches. Best practice: rebase feature branch lên develop trước khi merge (hoặc squash merge). `git rebase -i` để clean commits.",
    q_en: "How are git rebase and merge different? When should you use each?",
    a_en: "Merge: creates a merge commit, preserves full history, safe for shared branches. Rebase: rewrites history to be linear and cleaner — NEVER use on shared branches. Best practice: rebase your feature branch onto develop before merging (or use squash merge). `git rebase -i` for cleaning up commits interactively.",
