    a: "`class EventEmitter { constructor() { this.events = {}; } on(event, fn) { (this.events[event] ||= []).push(fn); } off(event, fn) { this.events[event] = this.events[event]?.filter(f => f !== fn); } emit(event, ...args) { this.events[event]?.forEach(fn => fn(...args)); } }` Pattern Observer, dùng trong state management, pub/sub systems.",
    q_en: "Implement a simple EventEmitter class.",
    a_en: "`class EventEmitter { constructor() { this.events = {}; } on(event, fn) { (this.events[event] ||= []).push(fn); } off(event, fn) { this.events[event] = this.events[event]?.filter(f => f !== fn); } emit(event, ...args) { this.events[event]?.forEach(fn => fn(...args)); } }` Implements the Observer pattern, used in state management and pub/sub systems.",
