    a_en: "(1) Do not rewrite everything at once. (2) Write all new components with hooks (100%). (3) When fixing a bug or adding a feature → convert that class to a function component. (4) Extract logic into custom hooks for reuse. (5) Class and function components coexist fine — no need to migrate everything. (6) Prioritize converting: HOCs → custom hooks, lifecycle methods → useEffect.",
